PN,39901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,FScientists have made a "significant
OL,7,Fstep" towards a blood test that
OL,8,Fdetects brain tumours and monitors
OL,9,Fthem in real-time.
OL,11,FThe new test is over 90% accurate and
OL,12,Fcould allow GPs to spot deadly
OL,13,Fglioblastomas early, with plans to
OL,14,Fexpand it to other brain tumours.
OL,16,FCurrently, diagnosis relies on complex
OL,17,FMRI scans and invasive biopsies, but
OL,18,Fthis uses two proteins in the blood
OL,19,Ffor high-accuracy detection and
OL,20,Ftreatment tracking.
OL,26,@nD@XOUoD@EO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
