OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,FThe study was led by University of
OL,7,FManchester Professor Petra Hamerlik,
OL,8,Fthe Brain Tumour Charity chair of
OL,9,Ftranslational neuro-oncology, working
OL,10,Fwith Danish teams.
OL,12,FPublished in Neuro-oncology Advances,
OL,13,Fit validated the test on glioblastoma
OL,14,Fpatients during surgery, radiotherapy,
OL,15,Fand chemotherapy.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,FProf Hamerlik said: "Glioblastoma is
OL,7,Fone of the most devastating cancers we
OL,8,Fface. What is remarkable is that,
OL,9,Fdespite these tumours being very
OL,10,Fdifferent in genetic make-up and
OL,11,Fconstantly evolving, the signal in the
OL,12,Fblood is stable, robust and highly
OL,13,Finformative."
OL,15,FShe hopes for a simple GP test - like
OL,16,Fa Covid swab - within a decade to fast-
OL,17,Ftrack MRI referrals for persistent
OL,18,Fheadaches.
OL,26,@nD@UOUuD@MO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
