OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,FThe breakthrough was announced just
OL,7,Fdays after the death of Phil Woolas,
OL,8,Fthe former Minister and MP for Oldham
OL,9,FEast and Saddleworth who died from
OL,10,Fbrain cancer.
OL,12,FHis family said he had suffered from
OL,13,Fthe symptoms of glioblastoma for more
OL,14,Fthan a year.
OL,16,FDr Simon Newman, chief scientific
OL,17,Fofficer at the Brain Tumour Charity,
OL,18,Fsaid: "Early and accurate diagnosis is
OL,19,Fabsolutely critical for people with
OL,20,Fbrain tumours, yet current tools are
OL,21,Flimited and often invasive.
OL,26,@zD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,F"This research therefore marks a
OL,7,Fsignificant step towards a simple
OL,8,Fblood test that could help clinicians
OL,9,Fdetect glioblastoma and monitor how
OL,10,Fpatients are responding to treatment
OL,11,Fin real time."
OL,13,FProf Hamerlik, whose father had
OL,14,Fglioblastoma, told the Press
OL,15,FAssociation people can often see a GP
OL,16,Fsix to eight times before being sent
OL,17,Ffor an MRI for a potential brain
OL,18,Ftumour.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,F"The idea with our work is that, if
OL,7,Fyou come more than once with a
OL,8,Fheadache, such as three times, and if
OL,9,Fthe doctor suspects a brain tumour,
OL,10,Fthey would run this test," she said.
OL,12,F"The risk score would indicate that
OL,13,Fyou might have a malignant growth in
OL,14,Fyour brain, and you should go for MRI.
OL,16,F"The idea is to develop a device `
OL,17,Fsomething like a Covid test ` to start
OL,18,Fwith.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@ZO]tD@AOUxD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,F"If this is confirmed, then it will be
OL,7,Fsubmitted to regulatory bodies and
OL,8,Fhopefully brought into the NHS within
OL,9,Fa decade."
OL,11,FProf Hamerlik said the test is also
OL,12,Feffective at measuring response to
OL,13,Ftherapy.
OL,15,F"When our patients started treatment
OL,16,Fafter surgery, the biomarkers
OL,17,Fchanged," she said.
OL,19,F"They went up as the tumour grew back,
OL,20,Fand then they went down again when
OL,21,Fpeople were having chemotherapy."
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@JO]wD@AOUyD@IO]{D@AOU}D@aO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,FThe team has launched a clinical trial
OL,7,Frunning at six sites in the UK and
OL,8,Ffour abroad.
OL,10,FAsked about the lack of treatments for
OL,11,Fglioblastoma, Prof Hamerlik said she
OL,12,Fwanted to be ready with a simple blood
OL,13,Ftest for when new medicines come on
OL,14,Fstream.
OL,16,FShe added: "Late diagnosis impacts the
OL,17,Fprognosis of the patients. The later,
OL,18,Fthe bigger the lesion, the worse the
OL,19,Foutcome.
OL,26,@xD@LOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
