OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,400,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F399A1773745530
OL,3,CNew blood test to detect brain tumours
OL,4,Cis 'highly accurate'
OL,6,F"Even with surgery, if the tumours are
OL,7,Fpicked up early and they're smaller,
OL,8,Fyou have less damage to the normal
OL,9,Fbrain."
OL,11,FA clinical trial is now underway at
OL,12,Fsix UK sites and four abroad, aiming
OL,13,Fto support future drugs by enabling
OL,14,Fearlier detection and better outcomes.
OL,16,FWant more on the issues affecting the
OL,17,FNorth? Our podcast, From the North
OL,18,Fanswers the questions that matter to
OL,19,Four region.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@GO]
